raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do random_post(\"campus_life\")
Mabel: Hey babe!
Player: Hey!
Player: You called me?
Mabel: Yeah!
Mabel: Naomi invited us both to the photography club room for a visit!!
Mabel: They said we're free to come by and hang out! There's gonna be a pizza and we can chat 🥰
Player: Wow you're all ready to go out now aren't you
Mabel: I don't understand it!!
Mabel: When she invited me I got so excited! 😳
Mabel: Naomi is SOOO easy to talk to tbh
Mabel: I feel like I get really chatty around her lol 😆
Mabel: Maybe I'm coming off as a little weird 🥹
Mabel: What do you think?
- I think she invited you cause she wants to be your friend! [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: I think she invited you cause she wants to be your friend!
	Mabel: I'm... wait really!?
	Mabel: She wants to be MY friend?
	Player: Why wouldn't she?
	Mabel: 😊 Idk... I just
	Mabel: Thought: AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
	Mabel: Hehe
	Player: You're acting kinda suspicious right now 😂
	Mabel: Sorry I'm just happy 😂
	Mabel: I feel like a kid on the playground who made her first friend LOL
	Mabel: Ahem 🧐 I mean..
- Don't lecture her on your James Bond theories and it'll be okay 😆 [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: Don't lecture her on your James Bond theories and it'll be okay 😆
	Mabel: What?? You really think so?
	Mabel: But you love listening to those!
	Player: She might not but who knows haha
	Mabel: I understand
	Mabel: I'll only tell her about the most important ones then 😓
	Player: 🤦‍♂️
	Mabel: I'M KIDDIIING 😂
Mabel: We're both invited btw
Mabel: Naomi told me her bf, Caleb doesn't have many friends!
Mabel: He said he'd be happy if you were to join too 😇
Mabel: We'll meet the others in their club too btw
Mabel: Oh right, what's the work situation?
Mabel: Do you have work on Saturday?
Player: No, my work is usually on Sundays
Mabel: Oh! Okay then!
Mabel: So you can come on Saturday??
Player: Yeah, I'm available
Mabel: 🥳
Mabel: I get to hang out with my baaabe ❤️
Player: 😊
Mabel: Maybe I'm asking for too much here but uhm
Mabel: Are you free on Sunday so, we can see each other?
Mabel: Y'know... maybe go on a date? 👉👈
- I can do that [#pinkheart]
	set Story.pink_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"SecondDate\"
	Player: I can do that
	if Story.pink_heart >= 2:
		Mabel: OMG ANOTHER DATE!!!
		do echo_set([\"52\"])
	Mabel: Is that okay??
	Mabel: Won't it be your first day of work?
	Player: Oh my work pays me if I show up 😆
	Player: No strict schedule!
	Mabel: Oh okay 🥰
	Mabel: I'm sorry for making you choose...
	Mabel: I appreciate the sacrifice 🥹 I really do
	Mabel: I hope I'm not in the way 😣
	- I'd skip every week of work for you 😘 [#love] [#trust]
		set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
		set Story.mabel_trust += 1
		Player: I'd skip every week of work for you
		Mabel: Jeez now you're just playing with my heart y'know 😍
		Mabel: PinkThought: I love you so much
		Player: 🥰
	- Money comes and goes, it's okay!
		Player: Money comes and goes, it's okay!
		Mabel: Thanks sweetie, it means a lot 😚
	do echo_clear()
- I have work [#dollar] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Week2Work\") == false]
	set PhoneUnlocks.claim = \"Week2Work\"
	Player: I have work
	do echo_set([\"53\"])
	Mabel: Oh okay, I don't want to ask for too much
	Mabel: Since you're already coming on Saturday
	Mabel: Don't push yourself too hard okay? 🥰
	Player: Thanks, I won't
- I have work [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Week2Work\") == true]
	Player: I need to work
	do echo_set([\"53\"])
	Mabel: Oh okay, I don't want to ask for too much
	Mabel: Since you're already coming on Saturday
	Mabel: Don't push yourself too hard okay? 🥰
	Player: Thanks, I won't
Mabel: Can't wait
Mabel: Naomi said she'd text you the details, so you can come get me and take us there 🥰
Mabel: This is gonna be the best weekend ever!
Mabel: Oh by the way, I have a LOT of homework due tomorrow 😅
Mabel: Might be busy
Mabel: So I'll talk to you tomorrow okay?
Player: Good luck then!
do echo_clear()
if Story.black_heart >= 4:
	do social_post(\"ninas_request\")
Mabel: Byeee, good night 😘
Player: Study hard!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
